OL,3,COutgoing police chief facing
OL,4,Cmisconduct investigation
OL,6,FThe police watchdog has confirmed an
OL,7,Finvestigation into a chief constable
OL,8,Fover alleged misconduct ` just a day
OL,9,Fafter he announced his retirement.
OL,11,FHumberside Police said on Tuesday, 25
OL,12,FJune, that Paul Anderson would be
OL,13,Fleaving the force's top job less than
OL,14,Fa year after his appointment.
OL,16,FThe force's official statement made no
OL,17,Fmention of allegations made against Mr
OL,18,FAnderson.
