OL,3,COutgoing police chief facing
OL,4,Cmisconduct investigation
OL,6,FBut on Wednesday, the Independent
OL,7,FOffice for Police Conduct (IOPC) said
OL,8,Fit had started an investigation after
OL,9,Freceiving a mandatory referral from
OL,10,Fthe office of Humberside Police and
OL,11,FCrime Commissioner (PCC) Jonathan
OL,12,FEvison two days earlier.
OL,14,FAn IOPC spokesperson said: "The
OL,15,Freferral, received on Monday (24 June)
OL,16,Fcontained allegations concerning
OL,17,Fstandards of behaviour, largely
OL,18,Frelated to communication and behaviour
OL,19,Ftowards colleagues.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/7
