OL,3,COutgoing police chief facing
OL,4,Cmisconduct investigation
OL,6,F"Confirmation was received by the OPCC
OL,7,Flate on Tuesday 25 June that the IOPC
OL,8,Fhad begun an independent investigation.
OL,10,F"Early yesterday it was announced that
OL,11,Fthe chief constable was retiring after
OL,12,F34 years of service.
OL,14,F"The IOPC investigation will continue
OL,15,Fnotwithstanding Paul Anderson's
OL,16,Fretirement. As this is now a live
OL,17,Finvestigation the PCC will make no
OL,18,Ffurther comment."
OL,20,F'He deserves much credit'
