OL,3,COutgoing police chief facing
OL,4,Cmisconduct investigation
OL,6,FThe latest statement from Mr Evison
OL,7,Fcomes after he issued a statement
OL,8,Fabout Mr Anderson's retirement, in
OL,9,Fwhich he said he had made "a valuable
OL,10,Fcontribution to the performance of
OL,11,FHumberside Police".
OL,13,FHe said: "Chief Constable Anderson
OL,14,Fdeserves much credit for that and I
OL,15,Fthank him for his service to the
OL,16,Fpublic."
