OL,6,FMr Anderson, who has a police career
OL,7,Fspanning 34 years, joined Humberside
OL,8,FPolice as an assistant chief constable
OL,9,Fin 2019 and was deputy chief constable
OL,10,Fbefore taking the role of chief
OL,11,Fconstable in 2023.
OL,13,FHe has yet to comment on the IOPC
OL,14,Finvestigation, but announcing his
OL,15,Fretirement he said: "It has been a
OL,16,Fprivilege to serve the communities of
OL,17,FHull, the East Riding, North and North
OL,18,FEast Lincolnshire.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/7
