OL,3,COutgoing police chief facing
OL,4,Cmisconduct investigation
OL,6,F"Humberside is an outstanding force
OL,7,Fmade up of both officers and staff who
OL,8,Fare dedicated to making a difference
OL,9,Fto the communities they represent. It
OL,10,Fhas been a difficult decision to make
OL,11,Fto retire from the force but it is the
OL,12,Fright time for me personally to make
OL,13,Fthis announcement."
